page.title: 20Thame Survey Credits
page.content: This Domesday survey has been carried out by the J4 children of St. Joseph's R.C. Primary. The children are..... Lucy Kinch, Claire Mackenzie, Claire Brown, Stephanie Gough, Paula Rolfe, Maria Farrugia, Katherine Tyler, Faith Russell, Emma Gardham, Cathrine Young, Sandra Mooney, Natalie Boshell, Helen coleman, Elaine Antoine, Fergus McVey, Daniel Stalder, Simon Vaux, David Rampley, David Boiling, Gavin Rowe and Tim Deasy. The class would like to thank Mrs.Jane McVey and Mrs. Maeve Aubele for making this project possible by giving up so much of their time to enable us to visit so much of our community. We would also like to thank all the people who showed us their places of work. We have all enjoyed working on the project. MN July 1985.
